OL,3,CMan admits killing 'loving, kind and
OL,4,Ccharming' pensioner
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has admitted killing
OL,7,Fa 'loving, kind and charming'
OL,8,Fpensioner in his home in Glastonbury.
OL,10,FJames O'Connor, from Hilltown, Dundee,
OL,11,FScotland, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,13,Fresponsibility at Bristol Crown Court
OL,14,Fon Thursday 8 February.
OL,16,FThe court was told how O'Connor
OL,17,Fstabbed 89-year-old Frederick Burge at
OL,18,Fhis home off George Street, in
OL,19,FGlastonbury, on Sunday 26 February
OL,20,F2023.
