OL,3,CMan admits killing 'loving, kind and
OL,4,Ccharming' pensioner
OL,6,FAt the time of his death, Frederick's
OL,7,Ffamily shared a tribute to the 'best
OL,8,Fdad, grandad, great-grandad and great-
OL,9,Fgreat-grandad in the world'.
OL,11,FThe statement they issued read: "He
OL,12,Fwas a loving, kind and charming man
OL,13,Fand a huge hole has been left in our
OL,14,Fhearts by his sudden passing.
OL,16,F"We take some comfort in knowing he is
OL,17,Fup in heaven with his late wife,
OL,18,FMarina, and he is looking down on us
OL,19,Fand we know he would want us to be
OL,20,Fstrong.
