OL,6,F"We will look back on the cherished
OL,7,Fmemories of the time we had together
OL,8,Fwith fondness, and we will treasure
OL,9,Fthese always."
OL,11,FDet Supt Gary Haskins, from the Major
OL,12,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "Our
OL,13,Fcollective thoughts remain with
OL,14,FFrederick's family, who have been
OL,15,Fsupportive throughout the
OL,16,Finvestigation.
