OL,3,CMan admits killing 'loving, kind and
OL,4,Ccharming' pensioner
OL,6,F"Frederick was described by them as a
OL,7,Fwell-known character in Glastonbury
OL,8,Fwith a friendly smile who regularly
OL,9,Fstopped to talk with others in the
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,F"We hope this result will give the
OL,13,Ffamily some closure and give them
OL,14,Fsolace following what has undoubtedly
OL,15,Fbeen a very difficult time.
OL,17,F"I would like to recognise the hard
OL,18,Fwork of all police officers and staff
OL,19,Finvolved in the investigation as well
OL,20,Fas partners within the community and
OL,21,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service."
